OL,4,CPROGRAMMES
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1999FBBC TV relaunches the news
OL,7,Foutput on BBC One and BBC Two (with the
OL,8,Fexception of Breakfast and Newsnight).
OL,9,FThe Lambie-Nairn agency designed the
OL,10,Fnew look title sequences and associated
OL,11,Fgraphics. The 1pm, 6pm and 9pm
OL,12,Fprogrammes (weekdays) and weekend
OL,13,Fprogrammes all shared the same studio
OL,14,Fset - which had a maroon/beige colour
OL,15,Fscheme, in line with the graphics
OL,16,Fpackage. David Lowe composed the new
OL,17,Ftheme tune.
OL,18,
OL,19,FPresenter-wise, Anna Ford would anchor
OL,20,Fthe 1pm programme, Huw Edwards fronted
OL,21,Fthe 6pm programme (the previous
OL,22,Fincarnation of the programme had two
OL,23,Sppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
